      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@\n+created: 2025-11-02\n+title: Changelog v0.6.0\n+intro: >-\n+  Refine release manifest format: rename 'description' to 'intro' and render it with\n+  a folded YAML block for better readability."
